cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.MA, cs.NE

This paper is about the application of evolutionary algorithms to optimize the design of soft robots for locomotion in different environments. This topic falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI), as well as systems and control (cs.SY) and machine learning (cs.MA) due to the use of optimization algorithms. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of neural networks for controlling the robots, which falls under the category of neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
